channel.description: Oh My Fucking God Guys.. I Know You Get This About 500 Time A Day.. But As You Can See I Been On Moparscape Community A Long Time Now And I Looked At About Every Guide There Is For This.. I CAN'T HOST!! I Fucking Got No-ip.com Downloaded And I Got My Own IP.. I Put It In Server And Compiled.. Then I Tryed The Damn Server And It Won't Let Any1 Connect And When i Go To "Canyouseeme.org" It Even Says It Is Offline.. WTF 0mfg I Tryed Everything I Had About 8-10 Previous Coders Try And Help Me With This Problem.. I Just Simply Can't Host!!!! OMFG I Am Making A Video Of What I Do To Try And Make My Server Online.. So You Can See Exactly What I Mean.. I JUST CAN'T HOST MY FUCKING SERVER... I Went Though Countless Guides So Meny I Don't Wanna Think About That Anymore.. I Search Online Asked Other Owners I Did Everything.. I Just Can't Afford A VPS Until 2 Years From Now.. I Want This Server Online NOW! Please Moparscape I Know your Just Thinking Whata Idiot.. But No I Got Everything Done.. I PortForwarded Correctly.. Got No Ip... Set Environmental Variables.. And Got Alot Of Help Before I Came To This.. Please Moparscape I Been Working On RSPS For Along Time Now.. Please I Really Deserve Just To Sit And Play On My Server With My Players.. Sorry About How Much Words There Are Lol ;) Anyways PLEASE HELP ME! Just Give Me Idea's Of What It Could Be... OR MOST OF ALL GET ON TEAMVIEWER AND HELP ME!! IF YOU WANT MY ID AND PASS JUST PM ME! Please Moparscape HELP ME! >>EDIT<< And I Let It Through Firewall!
